{"_id":"2PRXfVmOkuQKsLSO","name":"Norman Barrelchest","permission":{"default":0,"r4bmbG4VWpj9A47k":3},"folder":"wf40lADkdvhEIKuG","sort":2400000,"flags":{},"content":"<h1 dir=\"ltr\">Norman Barrelchest</h1>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">species, class</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">human fighter (soldier)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Occupation and history</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Constable for Marshbout</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Appearance</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Classic reversal, is slim as a blade of grass</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">missing a few fingers (which operate independently around the armory, and act as spies)</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">fingers are linked to him by &hellip;&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">long blonde hair in a loose braid&nbsp; horseshoe mustache (hard to tell if he&rsquo;s making it work), smokes some kind of hand-rolled cigarette</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">dressed to the nines</p>\n</li>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">brown frock coat with paisley vest and white shirt; brown trousers, conspicuous gold ring on right thumb</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Abilities</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">high strength, low constitution (hence skinniness, constitution:&nbsp; like losing/dropping his fingers and stuff, but very wiry)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Talent</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Mannerism</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">paces back and forth with chest out, but also hands and fingers protected</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">(prone to rage / argumentative) ?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Interactions with others</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Useful knowledge</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Ideal</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">respect, fairness, live and let live</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Bond</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Protective of a sentimental keepsake / valuable possession</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">maybe he&rsquo;s got his whole family&rsquo;s appendages</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Flaw or secret</h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">arms trafficking</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">knows about the Varts but does nothing</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">sister&rsquo;s activities</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">He&rsquo;s got the expanding creature (Zorbo) which also can do detect magic / identify on the objects, and these he sells to some in the exotic animals trafficking market, such as Tishara Vernix</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">also a &ldquo;Justice of the Peace&rdquo; &ldquo;Constable&rdquo; \"Marshall\"?&nbsp; -- or different name</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}
