000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">lightning starting to emerge from joan&rsquo;s mouth when she has to listen to Flick for too long</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;warm sense of nostalgia about the wordplay of half-elves&rdquo;</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">- a monastery montage - a mon...tage. monastage montagastery.&nbsp;</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">hub a dub dub , back to the hub</span></p>\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 10pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Proxima Nova',sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[24] famasta monastery</span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">3 floors, open courtyard with cobblestones, slate roof, big clocktower, gargoyles around , pale white stucco with windows, kind of institutional, magic stucco</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">flick &ldquo;Arrows are burning a whole in my pocket, since i haven't&rsquo; shot anything in an hour&rdquo;</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; col