e: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">flick: dreams that she has a pet that she forgot to feed for a week (lum)</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[57] firbolg&rsquo;s story. hated fey wild forest. and unbreakable contracts. research schools of magic (evocation, charm, transmutation).&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">joan&rdquo;does anyone feel like this is a benevolent dictator libertarian?&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">medicine check:&nbsp; - hands where holding staff: twisted and gnarled. extreme arthritis, or gout</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">we;re taught to think we&rsquo;re of the mountains, but we&rsquo;re not.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">raised to act like of the world, so had to poison selves, and most could sustain it, but he could not</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">over 1000 years old</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;would be willing to help stop that the plant-dogs can breach its sanctum&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;if you go north, druids live in forest; because they are attuned to woods, they and I have had relationships. if you let them know about the creatures, and tell you that I sent you, they might be more inclined to help&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[1:03]</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[do]: if i give them an emotional connection to a problem (Thuridan&rsquo;s hands); give them a way to solve it, or a side-quest, or something</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[do]: tie Raul to the Nightmare / Unicorn thing going on with the druds</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">gives Drav a spell leaf</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[1:09]</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">the magic of pr&rsquo;lll</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">thuriday: &ldquo;i remember the days when you could travel between celestial sphers in great magical zeppelins. in those days, too, there was a great evil in this land that was eradicated, but I suspect only temporarily. This figuring contains some of the magic of that evil. a demon sorcerer named Tantegorisch who ruled over this part of the world. Some sorcerers [did I mean &lsquo;warlocks&rsquo;?] draw their power from his scions. &ldquo;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;no, this symbol looks like it&rsquo;s contesting the power of Tantegorisch. it&rsquo;s keeping balanced in some way.&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[1:11]</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;to this day, some of the were creatures use this symbol to prevent themselves from metamorphosing at inopportune times.&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[1:13] carlos(jake) arrives</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">joan thinks the figurine prevents flick from were-shaping.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">flick &ldquo;tantalizing&rdquo; (tantegorisch-alizing?&rdquo;)</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">on the way back to castle karn (or, to there) with joan, drav, flick, flick is the one that sees the weird roots-in-the-air area of thuridan</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">===========</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[1:14:43] flick thinks Lupenna would like to get her hands on the statue, after Thuridan tells him about the werewolf stuff. (back in Cressida, Remi told him to look for Lupenna - &ldquo;Ratface McGillicutty&rdquo;).&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Cambria,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; fon