{"_id":"3gwkrul71GK2eScv","name":"Barazar Sod","permission":{"default":0,"akeJDKtMsE0KHFKm":3},"folder":"wf40lADkdvhEIKuG","sort":1600000,"flags":{},"content":"<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Barazar Sod</h2>\n<div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-4fc7e88d-7fff-ee51-f5bf-27d8690263b8\"></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">half-gnome</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">wealthy merchant</div>\n</li>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">middleman for some of the craft trades in town (cobblers, tailors, tinkers, smiths)</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">also trades along coast to import wine, textiles, spices for rare local items (troll bone powder)</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A member of the Worshipful Company of Mercers in the Valley of the Ponderous (or \"The Pond\" as everyone calls it).</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">patron (largely silent partner) of Dimpleweed&rsquo;s martial Academy</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">brother to Prehend Corvilla Sod</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">postures, outspoken, puts on airs of aristocracy, likes to refer to Corvilla&rsquo;s position, tho he has no idea what it is.&nbsp;</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">grew up in Cressida. Mother and father were in the local gentry ?&nbsp;</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">wears formal, clean, well-tailored clothes</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">thin and tall for a gnome, almost four feet tall, hair kept in a tight mohawk</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">blueish-purple, with a great forehead and delicate neck</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">wears a few simple rings</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">engaged to Sapora Brightmist, who currently resides north of Cressida in training as an Eldritch Knight and looking out for opportunities to open a knight&rsquo;s arm of Dimpleweed&rsquo;s Academy.&nbsp;</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">high intelligence, low wisdom (he&rsquo;s smart enough to put together the doings of the TMK, but not perceptive enough to watch out for himself -- his conclusions came from intelligence gathered by others)</div>\n</li>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">can be ponderous when he&rsquo;s talking about his mercantile and investment activities, but the idea of finding out the TMK plot really gets him going.</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">quite long-winded about Sapora</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">talent :&nbsp;</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">mannerism</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">ideals : Life, Responsibility, Balance</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">secret crime or misdeed</div>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">he&rsquo;s &ldquo;having a tryst&rdquo; with the Archaeologist (sapora is an agreed-upon cover, an old childhood friend from Cressida)</div>\n</li>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">is he using him, or -- he&rsquo;s also looking for mining opportunities</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>"}
