{"_id":"FNfFeSQy1G5iK9zN","name":"008. Blue dragon, candy, an accounting","permission":{"default":2,"akeJDKtMsE0KHFKm":3},"folder":"7FU7CCEBg8xZrzdi","sort":400000,"flags":{},"content":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3ae6b493-7fff-8738-1fe0-3c21da8ff7c7\"></span></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Session:</strong> &sect;008 Blue dragon, candy, an accounting</div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Played</strong>: December 14, 2019</div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a0776dae-7fff-2549-07ab-46e05a1bbbc3\"></span></strong></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Day 3 (cont.)</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Level 3</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><hr /></div>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Recap</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Confronted by Zachariel (a sap demon avenging a fancy piece of zorbo wood and her undesired individuation from glom^), Carlos attempted to answer her line of diversionary questioning regarding the unbelievable &lsquo;power&rsquo; of the original axe-wielder/perpetrator. Simultaneously, a nighthunter named Baba Jezda, having been roused by the breaking of the seals restraining Domonkos, manifested in the tunnel and fought the vampire; during the fight, a wild blow collapsed one of the walls, opening up a passage to a parallel tunnel in which flowed a slow back stream. Flick, shaking off a brief fantasy of running free, fast, and undetected forever, inquired of the two titans whatever was amiss between them. Consequently, she may have been the first to witness Mogh&rsquo;s unexpected emergence from Domonkos&rsquo;s back. The party split their attention between Zarachiel and the squiddybacking Mogh, and were soon joined by a quartet of gnomes led by one Polive Pittlans, a confectiergamist^ collecting some of the sweetest sap she&rsquo;d ever tasted tongue-wise. In a move as characteristic as it was unexpected, Carlos mended the wounded wood and with Polive&rsquo;s blessing returned Zarachiel whence she came. To help with the party&rsquo;s other front, Polive offered to retrieve a blue dragon wyrmling named Nexnag that she and the other gnomes had nursed from egghood. Domonkos rendered Nexnag superfluous after banishing Baba Jezda, but not before the nighthunter barricaded the way forward by creating a rock wall and marking it with an arcane rune. A lively discussion ensued between the gnomes, the party, and Domonkos as all decided where to head next, during which colloquy Polive offered Joan a cool bit of body mod for her nesethirls,^ Rihhilt praised Carlos&rsquo;s pacific tactics, Foldulf healed Wu&rsquo;un^ without magic and scrutinized Fez&rsquo;s administrations, and Paros foresaw an evil end in Nexnag&rsquo;s future.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-be91837e-7fff-865a-f181-2c25b9a4a90f\"></span></p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>&mdash; J. McClintock</strong></h4>\n<hr />\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-53b7a77c-7fff-b99f-94d3-74df71e66888\"><strong>glom</strong>: The &lsquo;we-sap&rsquo; or &lsquo;sap throng&rsquo; from which all sap demons emerge and to which all return.</span></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>confectiergamist</strong>: Candy maker.</div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>nesethirls</strong>: Nostrils.</div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Wu'un</strong>:&nbsp;[McClintock employs the unusual spelling \"Wu'un;\" the standard form 'Woon' is far more likely to be seen nowadays.]</div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><hr /></div>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Transcript</h2>\n<p>[n/a]</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p>[0-30]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[30]</p>\n<p>plot summary of session 007</p>\n<p>[40] rolling initiative</p>\n<p>[45] actually establishing order</p>\n<p>flick strings the bow</p>\n<p>{19} zarachiel would be amenable to talking</p>\n<p>slice out of the pole that you got the gravity orb from when carlos attacked it with his handaxe&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;oh yeah, that thing, sorry about that. what do you want. how can we make it up to you?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[48] interacting with Zarachiel</p>\n<p>&ldquo;my interest is in&nbsp; &hellip; . finding out what power you have that enabled you to do this.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>flick(jake): &ldquo;that pole wasn&rsquo;t one of your friends?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>zarachiel: &ldquo;i&rsquo;ve never seen the pole cut before, but few have attempted&rdquo;. &ldquo;the zorbo created the wood.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>came out of the sap that was oozing from the pole</p>\n<p>[51]</p>\n<p>Carlos goes to tell Zarachiel about his god (Aule)</p>\n<p>They hear the tearing noise of Baba Jezda coming in (hard to get eyes to focus on it -- able to look through the shape into space -- (&ldquo;classic problem [something] observer&rdquo;) of a shape where a body should be</p>\n<p>[x] jake &ldquo;it&rsquo;s not like it tried to materialize and failed to&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;all fez hears is this: &ldquo; [rousing action-adventure music]</p>\n<p>baba: &ldquo;did you think that both seals wouldn&rsquo;t attract my attention&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos &ldquo;this is one of the nighthunters&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[should have]: &ldquo;Why don&rsquo;t you introduce yourself, you mannerless piece of shit&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;looks like there&rsquo;s only one now, isn&rsquo;t there&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[should] nightwalker: &ldquo;i&rsquo;m doubtless all that&rsquo;s required now&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[x] don&rsquo;t use personal pronouns. say &ldquo;domonkos&rdquo; not &ldquo;he&rdquo;</p>\n<p>sap creature looks freaked the fuck out</p>\n<p>all of them can see the glowing eyes.</p>\n<p>flick had cast &ldquo;protection from good and evil&rdquo; on paros -- but haven&rsquo;t rolled saving throws since then</p>\n<p>[concerns] carlos (jenny): what if baba jezda turns on us afterwards if it kills/imprisons domonkos</p>\n<p>discussion of what the two seals were</p>\n<p>(remembering that Ecks attacked the squids with poison)</p>\n<p>[x] RIPX</p>\n<p>&ldquo;a long line of sap&rdquo; -- almost literally</p>\n<p>i said &ldquo;if there&rsquo;s a cut in the tree that we&rsquo;ve been made from, we manifest as a single organism&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[x] so that&rsquo;s kind of wrong -- they aren&rsquo;t made from the tree</p>\n<p>flick (jake) &ldquo;i want to know about his pancake powers&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[1:00]</p>\n<p>perception checks to see if they notice Zarachiel trying to get in their bodies<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span></p>\n<p>[x] i should determine who something is going after, and have just them do a perception check</p>\n<p>jake: &ldquo;is it because i asked about the pancakes?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[x] learn how to react to this from flick(jake) &ldquo;we ask permission before trying to feed each other maple syrup around here, buddy&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[x] also, if i have them roll the check, don&rsquo;t just let them take an action (necessarily), but make another check for what they want to do &hellip; ?</p>\n<p>[x] establish how close together people are (relative locations) before I do stuff like this, otherwise we end up negotiating that after the fact, and that&rsquo;s not great</p>\n<p>[x] if i have two or more npcs in a room, practice just them interacting with each other so i get a feel for personalities</p>\n<p>big sugar to get their talons in you</p>\n<p>flick(jake) flung against the wall for 6 HP</p>\n<p>syrup is delicious</p>\n<p>jake &ldquo;i was the friendliest one to this thing&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[x] that&rsquo;s a good point, i should explain that (like, she zarachiel thought she flick would be an easy sell)</p>\n<p>drav slows her down with ray of frost</p>\n<p>(soak up with spongy foost, caramelize him with fire)</p>\n<p>&ldquo;i hate being separated from my line, i&rsquo;ll do anything to get back to them&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[x] don&rsquo;t tell drav that he can&rsquo;t see the line of sap</p>\n<p>[1:06]</p>\n<p>chubby gnome scraping the sap into a tray, with 3 gnomes attending it</p>\n<p>joan: &ldquo;we shouldn&rsquo;t have had to make a perception check for that&rdquo;</p>\n<p>drav shouts out to the gnomes</p>\n<p>[callback joan] &ldquo;the sky turned black and it&rsquo;s raining rain blood&rdquo;</p>\n<p>mick: &ldquo;with the rainblood you can&rsquo;t see this far underground&rdquo;</p>\n<p>joan: &ldquo;how is a tree there?!&rdquo;</p>\n<p>polive &ldquo;collecting raw sugar for candy store&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[1:08]</p>\n<p>joan tries to pick up and move zarachiel</p>\n<p>joan crit fails, and sap creature gets a wet willy on her</p>\n<p>[x] sap demons turn from male to female when &hellip;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[1:12]</p>\n<p>fez tries to whip it</p>\n<p>[x] come up with a bunch of alternate ways of describing things (sap, sap, sap)</p>\n<p>carlos attacks it with the warhammer</p>\n<p>[1:14]&nbsp;</p>\n<p>carlos about to roll damage</p>\n<p>[x] (has an ability to concentrate its mass in different parts of its body, which is what the whip made it do, which is why carlos&rsquo;s axe attack hit)</p>\n<p>[1:15]</p>\n<p>jake (to mick): wait, what&rsquo;s your class? mick -- hard to say. i&rsquo;m a sailor</p>\n<p>domonkos fighting nighthunter</p>\n<p>paros hits it with some heat, so it speeds up again</p>\n<p>[...]</p>\n<p>[1:48]</p>\n<p>Domonkos doesn&rsquo;t know that MOGH is back there.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[x] should get checked for MOGHes each year.</p>\n<p>[1:51]</p>\n<p>Carlos convinces Polive to let her try to force Zarachiel back into the wood by casting mending on it</p>\n<p>Zarachiel sucked back up into wood</p>\n<p>Carlos hands wood back to Polive</p>\n<p>jake: &ldquo;they&rsquo;re not going to be able to get it out&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[1:54]</p>\n<p>Carlos: &ldquo;before I hand them the log, I ask for candy&rdquo;</p>\n<p>RIHHILT (the magic user): I&rsquo;ve never seen any of this &hellip; despite what Polive&rsquo;s every got from the traders, i&rsquo;ve never seen a cut piece of wood,&nbsp; like this, truly. not cut wood or sap, certainly not of this makeup.&nbsp; i&rsquo;d be more than willing to learn what you have to teach us, and give you a tour of the candy factor.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[1:55]</p>\n<p>jake: ask them if they think candy will help settle the dispute.</p>\n<p>polive: no, candy won&rsquo;t do anything, but we do have a friend who might be able to do something.</p>\n<p>(polive rushes into the back)</p>\n<p>RIHHILT : we&rsquo;ve been doing something kind of against our wishes [better judgment] training a , um --- a wyrmling</p>\n<p>[1:56]</p>\n<p>paros --- firebolts the mogh and kills it.</p>\n<p>[1:58]</p>\n<p>polive comes back in pulling matte blue dragon wyrmling : NEXNAG looks very happy. wagging her tail ([thrashing her tail])</p>\n<p>she does tricks for candy snacks. sit, hover,&nbsp;</p>\n<p>candied sap; bloodcake</p>\n<p>[2:01]</p>\n<p>RIHHILT comes up to carlos: &ldquo;that was truly amazing what you did back there. i like how it involved [...] healing. is that how you approach your life in general?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[improve] &ldquo;is that your approach to life ?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:02]</p>\n<p>jake: &ldquo;are these the deep gnomes we heard about&rdquo;</p>\n<p>zach: &ldquo;probably unusual for different groups of gnomes to live this close together&rdquo;</p>\n<p>jenny: &ldquo;are they made of candy?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:03]</p>\n<p>carlos&rsquo;s fantasy: thinking fondly of rescuing a &ldquo;thirsty&rdquo; gnoll &ldquo;princess&rdquo; from the gnomes</p>\n<p>[2:05]</p>\n<p>carlos asks RIHHILT if they know anything about a gnoll princess.</p>\n<p>(&ldquo;it&rsquo;s the G-gnoll&rdquo;)</p>\n<p>RIHHILT: people who don&rsquo;t fit in in gnoll society occasionally come and spend time with us, to take part in the sweeter arts of life</p>\n<p>carlos: &ldquo;are any gnolls present in of your society?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>rihhilt: &ldquo;there aren&rsquo;t any that are part of the society, but i think there are some back at the main town, right nowthere are usually a few passing through&rdquo;</p>\n<p>carlos rolls perception [17] to see if RIHHILT is lying.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>dm: &ldquo;she doesn&rsquo;t seem like she&rsquo;s lying&rdquo;</p>\n<p>carlos is confused about whether or not to like her.</p>\n<p>[2:07]</p>\n<p>flick&nbsp;</p>\n<p>mogh dead, dry on ground</p>\n<p>DOMONKOS - open sore on back, still fighting nighthunter</p>\n<p>flick&rsquo;s passing / fleeting imagery</p>\n<p>jake: are there still pieces of the nighthunter floating around?</p>\n<p>dm: they&rsquo;re pretty much dissipated</p>\n<p>flick (jake) : &ldquo;can&rsquo;t you all just get along; and, if not, state your positions&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:09]</p>\n<p>flick: &ldquo;that sucks for him, why would you want to do that?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:10]</p>\n<p>paros (nat 20 on insight into Domonkos) - he&rsquo;s remembering the last time he fought baba jezda -- between the two of them they slaughtered everyone, as collateral damage. she appeared as soon as he appeared at the monastery. there were more of her than just one. you can&rsquo;t tell because they kind of merge into each other.they dragged him back to the cave and re-installed him there.</p>\n<p>flick (jake) &ldquo;you guys should take it easy and let&rsquo;s go eat candy&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos: when i&rsquo;m done with her, i&rsquo;d love some candy , if you want to get in on this with me</p>\n<p>nighthunter: &ldquo;no, thank you, i don&rsquo;t eat. even candy, i can&rsquo;t eat.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>fez: &ldquo;i thought you said you had this ihandled, Domonkos&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos: &ldquo;maybe it looks like things aren&rsquo;t going my way&rdquo;</p>\n<p>fez: are you requesting our help?</p>\n<p>domonkos: &ldquo;yes, and i&rsquo;m not proud of it. it looks like mogh drained me more than i thought&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;something&rsquo;s been taken from me&rdquo;</p>\n<p>(ecks is still here)</p>\n<p>[2:13]</p>\n<p>flick insight check on nighthunter. [14] you don&rsquo;t know why nighthunter isn&rsquo;t trying to kill him; you think there might be leeway there.</p>\n<p>flick (jake) can we gauge who&rsquo;s more powerful?</p>\n<p>dm: she does; when domonkos got first sip, may have helped him, but now he&rsquo;s foundering.</p>\n<p>[2:15]</p>\n<p>domonkos eyes blaze white; reminds you of when looked at paros that one time.</p>\n<p>&ldquo;begone!&rdquo; - pushed back 20 feet. reaches up to cave roof and pulls down the rock like you&rsquo;d pull down a shade or roll-down security door. glowing backwards C appears on this wall, and she&rsquo;s behind it.</p>\n<p>burns brightly and fades out</p>\n<p>fez makes intelligence check to see if rune looks familiar</p>\n<p>paros too ?</p>\n<p>[2:17]</p>\n<p>paros asks domonkos what deal is with the backwards-C</p>\n<p>symbol of Kha; one of things preventing me from getting out of cavern before. together with Ecks, they render me much less powerful; in combination they are often used . she&rsquo;s capable of bringing both of them into existence.</p>\n<p>[anal scent glands or not]</p>\n<p>&ldquo;the C door&nbsp; is moved back to here, now?&rdquo; matt&nbsp; (&ldquo;see door&rdquo;?)</p>\n<p>[2:21]</p>\n<p>[i&rsquo;m out of the room; talking about greyhounds and whippets]</p>\n<p>[2:23] im back</p>\n<p>&ldquo;i heard that demon [Zarachiel] mention a Zorbo&rdquo; --&nbsp;</p>\n<p>zorbo story : joan tried to hug it, but the zorbo thought she was trying to attack it</p>\n<p>fez rolls to see if he has any idea what a zorbo is</p>\n<p>&ldquo;you think it&rsquo;s a letter of the alphabet&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:25]</p>\n<p>RIIHILT: is told where zorbon can be found (the pole one, and maybe the bridge one?)</p>\n<p>i&rsquo;m thrice in your debt</p>\n<p>flick: &ldquo;no biggie&rdquo;</p>\n<p>flick to domonkos: &ldquo;do you want to go to the candy factory&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos: &ldquo;stopping in a candy factory wouldn&rsquo;t be ideal&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos: i&rsquo;ve said thank you so many times!</p>\n<p>joan: &ldquo;we&rsquo;re also his best friends!&rdquo;</p>\n<p>carlos: &ldquo;can i lesser restoration the enchantment off of him?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>paros: &ldquo;i want to persuade him to come with us to the candy factory&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos: &ldquo;there&rsquo;s no reason i&rsquo;m not going to go over there with you&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;so you all want to go backwards?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;i did smell what i&rsquo;m pretty sure was bloodcake being fed to that wyrmling&rdquo;</p>\n<p>paros: &ldquo;you can even put candy on it.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos: &ldquo;i take everything I know from experience!&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:30]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;joan, you know that you (even as a bronze dragon) and the blue dragon wyrmling can both spit lightning from your mouths</p>\n<p>carlos: &ldquo;do you feel like your brethren has been imprisoned as a pet?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>joan: &ldquo;sure, yeah&rdquo;</p>\n<p>flick (jake) : he seems happy</p>\n<p>drav: &ldquo;he&rsquo;s being fed bloodcakes&rdquo;</p>\n<p>NEXNAG comes up and nuzzles at Joan&rsquo;s chest. 5&rsquo; at shoulders.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[2:31]</p>\n<p>the nostril muzzle nostrils have a kind of muzzle&nbsp;</p>\n<p>joan: &ldquo;why this?!&rdquo;</p>\n<p>polive: &ldquo;it requires less of her energy to breath lightningn onto poeple. and it&rsquo;s less wear and tear on her when she can channel lightning through her&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;they aren&rsquo;t difficult to make&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;we do owe you a favor (technically to carlos&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;let&rsquo;s head back to the candy lab&rdquo;</p>\n<p>mick: &ldquo;we&rsquo;re about to walk in there and get murdered into candy&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&ldquo;it&rsquo;s a breath-right strip&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:34]</p>\n<p>will really take some work to get Domonkos to go to candy mountain</p>\n<p>[x] looks a bit like a steam boiler safety valve?&nbsp;</p>\n<p>PAROS: &ldquo;are they saying this in a weird way (insight [N20])</p>\n<p>looks like he&rsquo;s looking a gift dragon in the mouth</p>\n<p>[x] i guess i didn&rsquo;t really answer paros about offering the nose thing</p>\n<p>dm: &ldquo;you feel like you want to do good things for the world. you feel like you gave something up. this dragon feels similar, will have to give something up, for its life now&rdquo;</p>\n<p>as far as offering joan the body mod, that seems legit. (they aren&rsquo;t going to feed a dragonborn to a dragon)</p>\n<p>fez: &ldquo;all the dragons are connected&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:36]</p>\n<p>paros&rsquo;s sorceros origin is from bronze dragon.</p>\n<p>[2:37]</p>\n<p>foldulf (he), with the scar and the blue hair goes over to Wu&rsquo;un (her) and applying salves and ointments.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>insight check: carlos, fez: looks like a familiar action. isn&rsquo;t accompanied by divine or arcane phenomena?&nbsp; (augmentations, attributes, enhancements, flourishes, embellishments, )</p>\n<p>particularly to fez, but there&rsquo;s a little pep in you when you pull the same thing off.</p>\n<p>polive: are we going to candy lab?</p>\n<p>fez &ldquo;heals&rdquo; self for 15 (with medicine kit) fish oil ointment -- they smell not great.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>FOLDULF : &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t think the balm is magical, I just know what I&rsquo;m doing.&rdquo; to carlos: &ldquo;it took a while for me to teach myself; when you&rsquo;ve gone through what I have you learn to rely on yourself&rdquo;</p>\n<p>carlos: this guy has magical healing and candy, i want to be best friends with him.</p>\n<p>[2:41]</p>\n<p>domonkos: &ldquo;i&rsquo;m not sure what it&rsquo;s doing right now&rdquo; (referrin to Ecks), the insignia ( C ) is keeping me here, but if I destroy Ecks they&rsquo;ll just send someone else</p>\n<p>flick: &ldquo;your back&rdquo;</p>\n<p>domonkos: looks through Ecks:&nbsp;</p>\n<p>did one of you bumbling buffoons do this to me ?</p>\n<p>paros: this was just the mini-mogh; sounds the same but it&rsquo;s smaller</p>\n<p>domonkos: &ldquo;sounds like an excuse for someone firing a blood bolt at me&rdquo;</p>\n<p>paros: &ldquo;would i lie to you?&rdquo;</p>\n<p>flick: &ldquo;we killed it off your back&rdquo;</p>\n<p>jake: &ldquo;what if it was an illusion that the guy (nighthunter) created, and we all saw it, and we were shooting domonkos and doing damage to him the whole time</p>\n<p>paros: but it&rsquo;s on the floor</p>\n<p>fez shows him the husk</p>\n<p>domonkos: mini-mogh, sure. &ldquo;paros, you&rsquo;ve been a great friend to me. it&rsquo;s tough for me to believe that naythin so pitiful could have drained me &ldquo;</p>\n<p>fez: &ldquo;at one poin during the fight, it got some constellationy things&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[x] Paros-sitizing me</p>\n<p>domonkos calls the gnomes evil; &ldquo;well I don&rsquo;t know: last I knew they were evil&rdquo;</p>\n<p>flick: &ldquo;they&rsquo;re trying to rebrand&rdquo;</p>\n<p>dom: &ldquo;everyone should be able to re-create themselves, no matter how short they are or evil they once were&rdquo;</p>\n<p>[2:46]</p>\n<p>Domonkos: asks polive for Cake. &ldquo;not on me&rdquo;, visiting your fabrication factory doesn&rsquo;t interest me. you&rsquo;re welcome to join me.</p>\n<p>paros (i thought i could convince domonkos to come with us)</p>\n<p>&ldquo;if this one promises me some bloodcake, i could take a short detail&rdquo;</p>\n<p>paros: &ldquo;i&rsquo;m just helping you out to get your bloodcake&rdquo;</p>\n<p>polive: &ldquo;welp, then follow us!&rdquo; and they turn around and start heading right back to the cavern.</p>\n<p>[2:48] end of session</p>\n<p>fez finds self singing song about the mountains</p>\n<p>POLIVE tells him about the grey tongue that was once a mountain, and the gods sliced it off at the base, and the peak became &hellip; it crumbled into the shore, and it was used to enlarge the area of the shore, and reduce the sea.&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>recording 2</p>\n<p>[0]</p>\n<p>carlos: what if they&rsquo;re good forces for controlling this evil dragon ?</p>\n<p>ian: mutually beneficial relationship with the gnomes ?</p>\n<p>jake: that&rsquo;s what he was hinting at, saying they have magic that you can&rsquo;t perceive as magic. (like harry potter house elves)</p>\n<p>debi : why does it have to be evil?</p>\n<p>jake: that&rsquo;s just the rules.</p>\n<p>jake: gnolls are supposed to be evil, too ?&nbsp;</p>\n<p>angela: i completely forgot about paros &hellip; domonkos &hellip; killing everyone in the monastery</p>\n<p>jenny: i don&rsquo;t know who to trust</p>\n<p>jake: but it was by accident&nbsp;</p>\n<p>angela: domonkos &hellip; night hunter .</p>\n<p>jke: they said it was true that there are random gnolls hanging out --- good indication that they aren&rsquo;t hostages</p>\n<p>[5]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</section>"}
